    "Id": "vehicledef_MANTICORE",
    "Name": "Manticore Heavy Tank",
    "UIName": "Manticore Heavy Tank (Standard)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Manticore Heavy Tank</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Standard </color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>240 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Manticore is one of the most powerful and well-designed tanks ever created. While not matching the raw firepower of super-heavy vehicles like the Demolisher or Behemoth, its combination of heavy armor and diverse weaponry makes it a highly effective platform against most threats.\n\nThe tank's main weapon is a Particle Projector Cannon, backed up by SRM-6 rack mounted just behind it. The SRM is mounted on vertical and horizontal swivel mounts, giving it a full 120-degree arc of fire independent of the turret. Both weapons are supported in their respective range brackets by an LRM-10 and Medium Laser.",
